posting_body: ['Welcome to Town Centre', 'Rental Information', 'Pricing:', '$2090/Month | 3 Bedroom 2 Bath | 1595 sq ft', 'Lease Term:', 'Variable', 'show contact info', 'Apartment Amenities', '− Air Conditioning', '− Dining Room', '− Ice Maker In Select Homes', '− Linen Closet', '− Microwave', '− Vaulted Ceiling In Select Homes', '− Views', '− Washer/Dryer Included', '− Wheelchair Accessible (Rooms)', '− Wood Burning Fireplace', 'In Select Homes (3rd Floor Only)', 'Community Features', '− Cardio Machines', '− Disposal Chutes', '− Fitness Center', '− Free Weights', '− Picnic Area', '− Pool', '− Recycling', '− Smoke-Free', '− Views', '− Walking Trails', '− 24 Hour Availability', '− Controlled Access Building', '− Intercom/Call Box', '− Off-Street Parking', '− On-site Maintenance', '− Planned Social Activities', '− Reservable Clubhouse', '− Video Surveillance', '− Volleyball Court', '− Yoga Studio/Room', 'About Community', 'Description:', 'We designed our apartment homes and floor plans with your comfort in mind, with beds ranging from one-bedroom, a larger two-bedroom, or a spacious three-bedroom apartment model.', 'The extra beds make great home offices, too.', 'Enjoy the view of Eagan from your balcony, relax in the community clubhouse, exercise in the fitness center, or swim in the pool.', 'Life in our community includes the comforts of a small town with the benefits of the city and the MN outdoors from your doorstep.', 'Location:', '3475 Golfview Dr', 'Eagan, MN 55123', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Additional Information', 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $250.00, Rent $30.00, Deposit $250.00.', 'Breed Restrictions Apply.', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Our Management Company:', 'Weidner Apartment Homes, LLC', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'DA05FEDA9BC044']
